BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Living with chronic pain is exhausting, isolating, and often misunderstood. This workbook) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (is designed to be your daily companion in managing pain - not just surviving it, but) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (building a meaningful life alongside it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (You will learn evidence-based strategies for tracking triggers, managing flare-ups,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (communicating with healthcare providers, and finding what works for YOUR unique pain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (experience.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 582.4 Td (Who This Book Is For) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.4 Td (- People with chronic pain lasting 3+ months) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (- Those with fibromyalgia, arthritis, or back pain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.4 Td (- Anyone managing pain alongside medical treatment) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (- People seeking non-pharmacological pain tools) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
