BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 3: Pain Management Strategies) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (The Pain Management Toolbox) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (No single strategy eliminates chronic pain. The goal is building a diverse toolbox of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (techniques that together help you manage pain and improve function.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 614.4 Td (Pacing: Your Most Important Tool) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.4 Td (Pacing means balancing activity and rest to avoid the boom-bust cycle:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Boom: On good days, overdoing it because you feel better) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Bust: Days of increased pain and forced rest afterwards) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Pacing: Consistent moderate activity regardless of pain level) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 528.6 Td (How to Pace) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512.6 Td (- Find your baseline: The activity level you can do WITHOUT a flare-up) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.6 Td (- Set time limits, not completion goals) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.6 Td (- Take breaks BEFORE pain increases) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.6 Td (- Gradually increase by 10% per week only when stable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.6 Td (- On good days: Do the same amount, not more) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 426.8 Td (Graded Exposure) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 408.8 Td (Gradually reintroduce activities you've been avoiding due to pain:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 394.8 Td (- List avoided activities in order of fear/difficulty) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.8 Td (- Start with the easiest, do a small amount) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366.8 Td (- Notice: Did the feared consequence happen?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.8 Td (- Gradually increase as confidence builds) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 323.0 Td (Acceptance-Based Approaches) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 305.0 Td (Acceptance does not mean giving up. It means stopping the fight against pain and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 291.0 Td (redirecting energy toward living well despite pain.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 277.0 Td (- Acknowledge pain without judgment) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 263.0 Td (- Focus on values and what matters to you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 249.0 Td (- Take action toward goals even with pain present) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 235.0 Td (- Practice willingness to experience discomfort) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
