BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 5: Movement & Physical Therapy) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Why Movement Matters) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Movement is medicine for chronic pain. It may seem counterintuitive, but gentle,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (consistent movement actually reduces pain sensitivity over time by retraining the nervous) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (system.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 600.4 Td (Gentle Movement Options) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Walking: Start with 5 minutes, increase gradually) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Swimming/water therapy: Joint-friendly, soothing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Yoga: Gentle/restorative classes \(not power yoga\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (- Tai Chi: Slow, flowing movements, proven for pain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.4 Td (- Stretching: Daily gentle stretches for affected areas) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514.4 Td (- Pilates: Core strengthening, modified for pain) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 486.6 Td (Movement Principles for Chronic Pain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.6 Td (- Start below what you think you can do) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.6 Td (- Consistency over intensity \(daily small amounts\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.6 Td (- Some discomfort is okay; sharp or escalating pain means stop) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 428.6 Td (- Progress slowly \(10% increase per week maximum\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 414.6 Td (- Never compare to pre-pain abilities) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 400.6 Td (- Celebrate every minute of movement) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 370.8 Td (Daily Gentle Stretching Routine) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.8 Td (- Neck rolls: Slowly circle head 5x each direction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 338.8 Td (- Shoulder shrugs: Lift shoulders to ears, hold 5 sec, release x10) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 324.8 Td (- Cat-cow stretches: On all fours, arch and round spine gently x10) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 310.8 Td (- Knee-to-chest: Lying down, pull one knee to chest, hold 30 sec each) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 296.8 Td (- Child's pose: Kneel, sit back on heels, arms forward, hold 1 min) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 282.8 Td (- Gentle twist: Seated, twist to each side gently, hold 30 sec) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 268.8 Td (- Hamstring stretch: Seated, reach toward toes, hold 30 sec) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 254.8 Td (- Hip flexor stretch: Lunge position, hold 30 sec each side) Tj ET
endstream
